Revision history for Term::Choose::Util


1.3.6   2021-08-12
        - Removed option 'enchanted'.
        - New undocumented options.
        - Update 'choose-directories'.
        - Update 'choose-a-file'.
        - Bugfix 'line-fold' 'subseq-tab'.
        - Change scope of Term::Choose.

1.3.5   2021-05-29
        - Bugfixes in 'choose-a-number', 'choose-a-subset' and 'choose-directories'.
        - choose-a-number: new option 'default-number'.

1.3.4   2020-04-02
        - Removed deprecated functions.
        - Update option cs-label.
        - Update choose-directories.
        - Update choose-a-file.
        - Update choose-a-number.
        - Update settings-menu.

1.3.3   2020-02-22
        - Speed up test. Fix typo. [ GH #2 JJ ]

1.3.2   2020-02-20
        - Update 'choose-directories'.

1.3.1   2020-01-26
        - choose-a-file: new option 'filter'.
        - Rewritten 'choose_directories'.
        - Bugfix color-output in 'choose-a-number'.
        - Set the option 'color' to 2 to enable colors also for the current selected item.

1.3.0   2019-10-30
        - Renamed functions: 'choose-a-dir' to 'choose-a-directory', 'choose-dirs' to 'choose-directories'.
        - New option 'color';
        - Renamed some options.
        - 'settings-menu': looping through values only once.
        - Update menus.
        - Update documentation.

1.2.9   2019-06-06
        - Update settings-menu behavior.
        - Pass clear-screen to Term::Choose

1.2.8   2019-06-02
        - Escape sequence subroutines without print.
        - Perl6 minimum version 6.d.

1.2.7   2019-05-20
        - From clr-to-bot to clr-lines-to-bot.
        - Update loop.

1.2.6   2019-05-07
        - Term::Choose minimum version 1.5.3.

1.2.5   2019-05-07
        - Bugfix values count in settings-menu.
        - Bufix options init_term.
        - Option loop.

1.2.4   2019-04-02
        - Use the alternate screen by setting the option 'clear-screen' to 2.

1.2.3   2019-03-26
        - Update META6.

1.2.2   2019-03-26
        - No changes.

1.2.1   2019-03-26
        - Update travis.

1.2.0   2019-03-26
        - From ncurses to ANSI escapes.
        - Added documentation for new options.

1.1.3   2019-02-28
        - New experimental options.
        - Renamed experimental options.

1.1.2   2018-08-24
        - First upload to CPAN
        - No changes

1.1.1   2018-06-27
        - "no-spacebar" to "meta-items"

1.1.0   2018-04-29
        - Removed option "current-..."
        - "choose-a-number": new option "small-on-top"
        - "choose-a-subset": new options "remove-chosen", "mark", "fmt-chosen"
        - Reset "choose-a-subset" and "choose-dirs" step by step
        - Update documentation

1.0.7   2018-02-19
        - Removed deprecated option "in-place"
        - Bugfix in reset numbers

1.0.6   2018-01-18
